title: Jet Li Movie Collection [1982-2008][EngSub] - SaiyanWarrior
description:
IMPORTANT NOTES: 

*Most of these are English Hardcoded (HC), some of you may ask why hardcode?   Well, I hardcoded them because that's the way some people, including me, prefer it.  I apologise to those who would have rather me uploaded it without hardcoding.

*Avg Quality indicates that the quality is not great, but certainly watchable, and in my opinion much better than watching a bad English dub.

*Some of the English subs are pretty bad English...but I still think its more watchable than the dub versions.

*If you would like me to upload any of these files individually then please let me know in the comments and I'll do my best.  

*Please seed and please leave comments, whether its a thanks or some constructive criticism.

*I havent included the 2 documentaries that Jet Li were in, simply because the torrent is already pretty big.
